{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/Pixel_Banner_with_Cat.png?t=1736847944\" />You've just inherited your Grandpa's quaint typewriter store... but, there's a twist: you need to revamp this business for the modern world through custom keyboard designing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/Pixel_Leaves.png?t=1736847944\" />It's now your job to turn boards into coins. Design the keyboard of your dreams down to the individual key; apply skins, swap to custom key caps, mix in symbols, perfect your lighting &amp; challenge your imagination. Can you earn enough coins, manage your stock and unlock the best from the Capslock Catalogue?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/Pixel_Banner.png?t=1736847944\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/Key_Features.png?t=1736847944\" />Capslock is a casual game focused on design and testing your imagination. Choose between 130+ skins, 260+ custom keys, 270+ symbols and more to test your designs and make unique keyboards. Relax as you listen to the 'clicky' sounds to help you unwind and immerse into a keyboard building environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Start from scratch - solve the puzzle of dragging and dropping each key into its' slot to build out your keyboard, or dive straight into designing and auto-fill all your keys with the press of a button! You can edit one key at a time, or make changes to your whole board - Capslock moves at a pace which suits you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/Pixel_Leaves.png?t=1736847944\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/Stock_Management.png?t=1736847944\" />Capslock is a stock based game! The more boards you sell, the more coins you will have to explore the <i>&quot;Capslock Catalogue&quot;</i>. You will need to keep an eye on your stock levels and purchases to ensure your business stays profitable and you have access to the best content !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/Extras.png?t=1736847944\" />There are many features, big and small, to ensure complete freedom in designing a keyboard. Tweak each keys lighting or have fun with various RGB sequences. Rotate keys, write out your text, change keyboard &amp; background colours or try your designs out on multiple boards! Capslock is the tool to create your dream boards. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/Community.png?t=1736847944\" /><strong>Capslock is our first release from an indie team - it is our dream to create a keyboard designer community and listen to our players to enhance the game as it develops !</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/0001-0070.gif?t=1736847944\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/Pixel_Leaves_Banner.png?t=1736847944\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The KEY to new beginnings","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2931790/2bdeb9b9e3ef2badc4b033edfbf03d0191ebb693.jpg"},{"name":"Taking CTRL of business","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2931790/dc4a5a9c1065ebe9c436350abe322e1667a0fd23.jpg"},{"name":"SHIFTing your style","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2931790/9cd6bed582f900452bd1148d143b7ddb0f45e920.jpg"},{"name":"On BOARD with success","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2931790/b97eb58cb98986e514169e14c8cf4d201c63594c.jpg"},{"name":"ENTER your best performance","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2931790/9c3266afca295441e9e1acc1d9f0335e6364f489.jpg"},{"name":"That offer got CTRL-ALT-DELETED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2931790/60933739cd9a9874e88ffe7dc563546c8998fbe5.jpg"},{"name":"INSerting a lil light","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2931790/8c341706342d4b997267866103034d1841759bf4.jpg"},{"name":"HARDWIRED for greatness","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2931790/68226b205e7e455aac20ffeeec4113c2073857f6.jpg"},{"name":"KEYed up for victory","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2931790/aa5055634dc94ebd77198662af0d949fd53cd5e0.jpg"},{"name":"Time to flip the SWITCH","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2931790/ba30fb7e80d2431c7a528884109f17f29cfbd54d.jpg"}],"total":19},"background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2931790?t=1736847944","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2931790?t=1736847944","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736847944","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/